Package org.odpi.openmetadata.governanceservers.enginehostservices.admin

Class GovernanceServiceCache

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.governanceservers.enginehostservices.admin.GovernanceServiceCache
public class GovernanceServiceCache extends Object
GovernanceServiceCache maintains the information about a registered governance service. A single governance service may be registered using different request types.
